==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-æstɪk|-æstɪk]]

===Noun===
'''mastic'''

# An evergreen [[shrub]] or small [[tree]], ''[[Pistacia lentiscus]]'', native to the [[Mediterranean]].
# A hard, brittle, aromatic and transparent [[resin]] produced by this tree and used to make [[varnish]]es and [[chewing gum]].
# A flexible, waterproof [[cement]] used as an [[adhesive]], [[sealant]] or [[filler]].

